ArcelorMittal South Africa Sees Third Quarter Earnings Lower

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-27T05:10:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/arcelormittal-south-africa-sees-third-quarter-earnings-substantially-lower.html
ArcelorMittal South Africa Ltd. (ACL) , a
unit of the world’s largest steelmaker, said it expects to
report earnings for the third quarter that are “substantially
lower” than the previous three months.  The steelmaker commented in a stock exchange statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
